    BarInCreation.BarInCreationState
    This enumeration is used to define the current state of a barInCreation solution.

    It can take the following values :
    HARMONICRR : means that the solution is waiting the action of a HarmonicRR RYTHMEHRR : means that the solution is waiting the action of a RythmeHRR
